    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A term referring to the closure of a floor plan of a building or part of a building. Often used in reference to sacral architecture, especially church presbyteries or apses.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
